data.description: Priced right to sell. Don't hesitate on this one.  Will sell fast! A dream home with a beautiful front façade and master craft wood beams in vaulted dining room. Wood floors throughout the home.  Three bedrooms, with an upper loft bedroom or game room including a large closet plus attic entrance and storage.  The den is extra large with a fireplace and double doors to the lovely back yard. Custom kitchen cabinets with granite counter tops. If your dream is to own a Viking double oven Range, this is it.   1.5 year old metal roof. Rear yard access with detached two car garage. Washer, dryer and refrigerator to stay.  Owner is furnishing a 13 month home warranty to buyer.
